                "location": "India",
                "period": "July 2015 – June 2017",
                "description": "Developed advanced visualizations and user interfaces to analyze complex datasets, including network logs for security incidents, oceanographic data anomalies, and multilayer network patterns. Leveraged technologies such as D3.js, Python, C++, and Qt to create efficient, interactive tools that improved data interpretation and significantly reduced customer effort in building complex test cases."
              },
